    grammar: { title: `Would : demandes polies et habitudes passees`, content: `Would a plusieurs usages importants :

1. Demandes polies
Would you mind putting your phone away?
Would you like another coffee?

2. Propositions
I would put that off if I were you.

3. Habitudes passees (comme used to)
We would always take long walks on Sundays.

4. Conditions
I would take the job if the salary was better.

Formes :
would = 'd contraction
would not = wouldn't

Exemples naturels :
I wouldn't put up with that!
She'd take it back if she could.` },
